  "code": "sequenceDiagram\n  participant Client\n  participant API\n  participant DB\n\n  Client->>API: Request\n  activate API\n  API->>DB: Query\n  activate DB\n  DB-->>API: Rows\n  deactivate DB\n  alt success\n    API-->>Client: 200 OK\n  else failure\n    API-->>Client: 500 Error\n  end\n  deactivate API\n",
