  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个客户端调用API的流程图。场景是Client发请求给API，API再去查数据库，然后根据查询结果返回不同的响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "API",
        "DB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个参与者：Client、API和数据库。Client到API是同步请求吗？还有API查DB之后，返回给Client的结果需要区分成功和失败两种情况吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "API",
        "DB",
        "Request",
        "Query"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，API收到请求后要激活处理，然后同步查询数据库。数据库返回Rows之后API再判断，成功返回200，失败返回500。这两种情况要用alt分支画出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API",
        "DB",
        "Rows",
        "200 OK",
        "500 Error",
        "alt"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画主干流程：Client发起Request到API，激活API后发送Query给DB，激活DB后返回Rows，然后关闭DB的生命线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "API",
        "DB",
        "Request",
        "Query",
        "Rows"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，alt分支那里我补充一下：success分支是API返回200 OK给Client，failure分支是返回500 Error。两个都是虚线箭头表示响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API",
        "Client",
        "200 OK",
        "500 Error",
        "alt",
